An AR (Augmented Reality) Business Card is an innovative way to enhance networking by integrating digital elements into traditional business cards. Using a smartphone or AR app, 
users can scan the card to view interactive content like 3D models, videos, clickable links, or social media profiles.
Interactive Experience: Displays animations, product demos, or company presentations.
Contactless & Digital Integration: Instantly links to websites, portfolios, or appointment scheduling.
Personalized Engagement: Showcases a 3D avatar, QR codes, or virtual messages.
Memorable & Modern: Makes a lasting impression compared to standard business cards.
